headline: Fifth Third Appoints Mike Powell as Corporate Secretary
summary: CINCINNATI, February 26, 2025--Fifth Third (NASDAQ: FITB) today announced the appointment of Mike Powell as Corporate Secretary, effective immediately. Powell brings a wealth of experience in corporate governance, legal compliance, and administrative management to the role.
